85879.jpg','75g','1kg','½ tsp','300ml ','1','3','¼ teaspoon','225g','½ tsp','60g','60g','50g','2 tbs','','','','','','','','http://www.deliciousmagazine.co.uk/recipes/flamiche-flemish-leek-tart/','Tart','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vT0q5c880Rg',8,14);
