m over the omelette, then chill for up to 24 hrs.To serve, invert the omelette cake onto a serving plate and peel off the cling film. Pile rocket on the top and scatter over the cheese, a drizzle of olive oil and a little freshly ground black pepper. Serve cut into wedges.','Provençal Omelette Cake','https://www.themealdb.com/images/media/meals/qwtrtp1511799242.jpg','10','1 tbs','2 finely chopped','3 finely chopped','4','1 clove peeled crushed','1','300g','6 tblsp','4 tbs','2 tbs','to serve','to serve','','','','','','','','https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/6428/provenal-omelette-cake','Egg','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B7isFo2uP2k',8,14);
