'1/4 tsp','1','1','2 cups ','4','1','1 cup ','4 oz ','2 tbs','1','3 cloves','3','2 tsp','4 oz ','3 tbs','1/3 cup',' ',' ','https://www.allrecipes.com/recipe/78938/malaysian-nasi-lemak/',null,'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IUIs4C86Ilo',16,10);
